data.description: Live at the Corner of Happiness! A wonderful location for this well maintained Vinyl Sided Ranch that's set on a pretty corner lot found in a desirable Fausey neighborhood, close to Parks, Schools, highways & shopping! Featuring top of the line insulated doors from Window World, replacement windows, hardwood flrs in most rooms. A sun filled living room w/glistening wood flrs, a relaxing fireplace adds warmth to this spacious room flows into the expansive kitchen w/lots of cabinets & counter space, stainless appliances & a charming dining area. From the kitchen you can enjoy your summer nights sitting on the spacious 3 season Sunroom w/access to the pretty & private  fenced in backyard with patio, pool, & handy storage shed! You'll discover 3 generous bedrooms all w/roomy closets and plush wall to wall carpeting along with a sparkling updated tiled bathroom w/large walk in shower! As per WS Building Department there's Future Potential to Add a 2 car Garage! This is it!
